# Personal GCP auth (not Wayfair)

This workspace is a **personal** project on `skincare-trends-dev`. Do not use Wayfair credentials.

Before running dbt, `bq`, or Python ingest against BigQuery:

```bash
source scripts/use_personal_gcp.sh
```

Expected account: `yingjzhang02@gmail.com`  
Expected project: `skincare-trends-dev`  
Gcloud config name: `personal-codebase`

- **dbt** uses Application Default Credentials (ADC), not the gcloud active account.
- **`bq` CLI** uses the gcloud config selected via `CLOUDSDK_ACTIVE_CONFIG_NAME`.
- Global gcloud default may stay on Wayfair; this repo overrides via `scripts/use_personal_gcp.sh`.

If BigQuery returns `bigquery.jobs.create permission denied`, ADC is on the wrong account. Re-login:

```bash
gcloud auth application-default login --account=yingjzhang02@gmail.com \
  --scopes=https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform,https://www.googleapis.com/auth/bigquery
gcloud auth application-default set-quota-project skincare-trends-dev
```
